name: OSLogEntryFromProcess
desc: A protocol that defines subclasses containing metadata about a process.

items.name: var activityIdentifier: os_activity_id_t
items.desc: The activity identifier associated with the entry.

items.name: var process: String
items.desc: The name of the process that made the entry.

items.name: var processIdentifier: pid_t
items.desc: The process identifier that made the entry.

items.name: var sender: String
items.desc: The name of the binary image that made the entry.

items.name: var threadIdentifier: UInt64
items.desc: The identifier of the thread that made the entry.
